==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: bú shì lúshān zhēn miànmù
===Etymology===
Literally: unable to recognize the true face of [[wikipedia:Mount Lushan|Mount Lushan]]
===Idiom===
'''[[不识]][[庐山]][[真]][[面目]]'''
#  To not recognize someone when you see them (despite the fact that you should know who the person is).
===Alternate forms===
[[不識廬山真面目]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])
